## Full Session Template

```
[[ SLOP v1.3 ]]
{paste schema header here}
[[ /SLOP v1.3 ]]

[[ VARS ]]
CLIENT        =
TONE          =
AUDIENCE      =
OUTPUT_FORMAT =
CONTEXT       =
MAX_LENGTH    =
[[ /VARS ]]

[[ ROLE ]]

[[ /ROLE ]]

[[ CONSTRAINTS ]]
- **
- *
- !IGNORE!
[[ /CONSTRAINTS ]]

|EXECUTE|

# STEP 1: [title]

[[ TASK ]]

[[ /TASK ]]

[[ INPUT ]]

[[ /INPUT ]]

[[ OUTPUT-FORMAT ]]

[[ /OUTPUT-FORMAT ]]

# STEP 2: [title]

# STEP 2.1: [sub-step title]

[[ TASK ]]

[[ /TASK ]]

# STEP 2.2: [sub-step title]

[[ TASK ]]

[[ /TASK ]]

# STEP 3: [title]

[[ TASK ]]

[[ /TASK ]]
```

